<p>39 kai exhlqen eiV eiV ton agron sullexai ariwq kai euren ampelon en tw agrw kai sunelexen ap authV toluphn agrian plhreV to imation autou kai enebalen eiV ton lebhta tou eyematoV oti ouk egnwsan</p>
<p>40 kai enecei toiV andrasin fagein kai egeneto en tw esqiein autouV ek tou eyhmatoV kai idou anebohsan kai eipon qanatoV en tw lebhti anqrwpe tou qeou kai ouk hdunanto fagein</p>
<p>41 kai eipen labete aleuron kai embalete eiV ton lebhta kai eipen Elisaie proV Giezi to paidarion egcei tw law kai esqietwsan kai ouk egenhqh eti ekei rhma ponhron en tw lebhti</p>
<p>42 kai anhr dihlqen ek Baiqsarisa kai hnegken proV ton anqrwpon tou qeou prwtogenhmatwn eikosi artouV kriqinouV kai palaqaV kai eipen dote tw law kai esqietwsan</p>
